channel.title: Go Jetters
channel.desc: The Go Jetters are in the Monteverde Cloud Forest, exploring the trees and hoping for a glimpse of the beautiful quetzal bird. But upset over the disintegration of his trophy duster, Glitch causes havoc when he orders his Grimbots to search for the quetzal bird's feathers. Can the Go Jetters save a rare bird's nest and find a lost trophy.
